  "text": "The effect site remifentanil concentration was computed from the recorded dosing history using the pharmacokinetic and pharmacodynamic parameter set of Minto and colleagues. [CITATION_1] As stimulation and tracheal intubation were performed [mean (SD)] 11 (2.4) and 14 (2.5) min after induction of anaesthesia, respectively, the remifentanil concentrations were at steady state. Similar remifentanil concentrations could have been achieved with a target-controlled infusion system, although this would not have changed the concentration range and thus the overall results.",
